    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Ammonium salt made from a reaction of sulfuric acid and ammonia. It is primarily produced by the destructive distillation of coal. Ammonium sulfate is a commercially important chemical used as a fertilizer, food additive, and tanning agent.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
